message.entry: Input elements must be real integers.
Input elements must be either 0 or 1 for division over GF(2).
Input elements must be between 0 and P-1 for division over a prime field.
Input elements must be between -Inf and P^M-2 for division over an extension field.
Field parameter values must be real nonnegative integers.
Field parameter is not valid. See GFTUPLE.
Inputs must have the same size and orientation.
